		"description": "<p>At 14th level you become a true master of the undead. You may use a bonus action to command one undead creature which can hear you. The target must make a Charisma saving throw vs. your spell DC. On a failure, the undead creature becomes unable to attack you for one minute, and obeys your commands for the duration. The creature can make a new saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on a success.</p>\n<p>Once a creature succeeds in a saving throw against this feature, it becomes immune to the feature for 24 hours.</p>",
